Package com.google.appinventor.common.youngandroid Description

Constants related to the local http server used for communications between the Designer and Blocks Editor. Clients include:
  • com.google.appinventor.client.youngandroid
  • com.google.appinventor.server.project.youngandroid
  • com.google.appinventor.server.util
